      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Material properties (Ti-6Al-4V: E=114 GPa, nu=0.34) sourced from ASTM F136 and manufacturer certificates of conformance. UHMWPE block properties obtained from literature mean values. Geometric inputs derived from CMM measurements of physical specimens with documented uncertainty."
