      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "FEA model inputs mapped directly to experimentally measured specimen geometry and material lot properties. Correspondence between simulation inputs and physical test article parameters documented in the traceability matrix with quantified uncertainties."
    },
