      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness and structural failure load are the primary mechanical performance metrics specified in ASTM F1717 and are directly relevant to the regulatory submission context. QoI selection justified in the analysis plan with reference to the intended submission pathway."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
