      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Validation activities replicate the ASTM F1717 compression-bending protocol applied to the same device family and material system as the submission device. Validation domain overlap with the intended use domain assessed as high for geometry, loading mode, and material class."
    }
