    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) was reviewed and accepted based on the conservative nature of the single test condition and the consistency of model predictions across all 11 specimens. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the intended regulatory use.",
